snippet.title: Strength of the Sword 3 - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
A mechanical knight has been sent from the heavens to thwart a rising evil. Just a warning: that evil is wicked hard to fight, so prepare for a challenge.

Strength of the Sword 3 is out today on PS3.
